Frontier-Engineering Third-Party Notice
=======================================

This repository contains benchmark material that is original to
Frontier-Engineering and benchmark material that is copied, adapted, or derived
from third-party sources.

The repository-level third-party audit is maintained in:

  THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md

Standard third-party license texts used by the audit are stored in:

  LICENSES/third_party/

Before vendoring a new external repository, dataset, checkpoint, paper, or
competition asset, add its source, license, and required attribution to
THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md and place any required license text under
LICENSES/third_party/ or next to the vendored asset.

Important copyleft/share-alike notes:

- Robotics/CoFlyersVasarhelyiTuning contains GPL-3.0-derived benchmark material
  from micros-uav/CoFlyers.
- ComputerSystems/MallocLab contains CC-BY-SA-4.0-attributed teaching materials
  from PKUanonym/REKCARC-TSC-UHT.
- Optics tasks use GPL-3.0 packages such as OptiCommPy and diffractio as runtime
  dependencies; those packages are not vendored here.

Publication PDFs and competition images with unclear redistribution rights are
not bundled. Their folders contain citation or external-reference notes instead.

